---
/**
 * About Page
 *
 * Static page example.
 */

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Nestrokit">
  <div class="container py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Nestrokit</h1>
    
    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
        Nestrokit is a production-ready full-stack boilerplate designed for
        modern web development. It combines the best practices and tools to
        help you build scalable applications quickly.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Tech Stack</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Astro + Svelte 5 + Tailwind CSS 4</li>
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> NestJS + Prisma + PostgreSQL</li>
        <li><strong>Caching:</strong> Redis with ioredis</li>
        <li><strong>Auth:</strong> JWT with refresh tokens</li>
        <li><strong>API Client:</strong> orval for type-safe API calls</li>
        <li><strong>Monorepo:</strong> Turborepo + pnpm workspaces</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Architecture</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">
        The project follows a modular architecture with shared packages:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <li><code>@repo/config</code> - Shared TypeScript, ESLint, Tailwind configs</li>
        <li><code>@repo/core</code> - Domain types, schemas, errors</li>
        <li><code>@repo/utils</code> - Utility functions with fp-ts</li>
        <li><code>@repo/database</code> - Prisma client and repositories</li>
        <li><code>@repo/api-client</code> - Generated API client</li>
        <li><code>@repo/ui</code> - Shared Svelte components</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
